@using uh365898_db.Domain.Concrete
@using uh365898_db.Domain.Entities
@using uh365898_db.WebUI.Models
@model uh365898_db.WebUI.Models.ProductsListViewModel




<div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
        <div class="stepmenu">
            <ul class="breadcrumb">
                <li><a href="~/">Главная </a><span class="divider">/</span></li>
                <li><a href="~/Каталог">Каталог</a></li>

                @if (Model.CurrentCatz != null)
                {
                    <li><span class="divider">/</span>@Html.ActionLink(Model.CurrentCatz, "Shop", new { categzer = Model.CurrentCatz })</li>
                }
                else
                {
                <li></li>}

                @if (Model.CurrentCaton != null)
                {
                    <li><span class="divider">/</span>@Html.ActionLink(Model.CurrentCaton, "Shop", new { categzer = Model.CurrentCatz, categ = Model.CurrentCaton })</li>
                }
                else
                {
                <li></li>}


                @if (Model.CurrentCattw != null)
                {
                    <li><span class="divider">/</span>@Html.ActionLink(Model.CurrentCattw, "Shop", new { categzer = Model.CurrentCatz, categ = Model.CurrentCaton, twocateg = Model.CurrentCattw }) </li>

                }
                else
                {
                <li></li>}



            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
